        "content_1": {
          "type": "content_section",
          "settings": {
            "label": "About This Bundle",
            "heading": "Why UAE Parents Choose the Kids Dental Care Bundle",
            "subheading": "Everything your child needs for a complete oral care routine — in one box",
            "body": "<p>The Kids U-Shaped Brush Bundle brings together the three products UAE parents buy most into a single, money-saving set: the U-shaped electric toothbrush, strawberry foam toothpaste, and a pack of replacement silicone brush heads. At AED 150 you save over 51% compared to buying each item separately — and it all arrives with free next-day delivery anywhere in the Emirates.</p><p>The 360-degree U-shaped toothbrush cleans every tooth simultaneously in 60 seconds. The strawberry foam toothpaste fills every gap in the silicone head for maximum coverage — kids love the taste. And the spare brush heads mean you are set for months of healthy brushing without reordering. Choose from three colours (Orange, Pink, Blue) and two age groups (2-6, 7-12) so the fit is perfect for your child.</p><p>Parents across Dubai, Abu Dhabi, Sharjah and the rest of the UAE trust this bundle because it turns brushing from a daily battle into a routine kids look forward to. Cash on Delivery available on every order.</p>",
            "alt_bg": false
          }
        },
        "content_2": {
          "type": "content_section",
          "settings": {
            "label": "",
            "heading": "What Is Inside the Bundle",
            "subheading": "",
            "body": "<p><strong>1. Kids U-Shaped Electric Toothbrush</strong> — 360-degree food-grade silicone head wraps around all teeth at once. IPX7 waterproof, USB rechargeable, 30-day battery life. One-button operation even toddlers can manage.</p><p><strong>2. Kids Strawberry Foam Toothpaste</strong> — Natural strawberry flavour kids actually enjoy. Fluoride-free formula safe if swallowed. The foam expands to fill every groove in the U-shaped head for thorough cleaning.</p><p><strong>3. Replacement Silicone Brush Heads</strong> — Dentists recommend replacing brush heads every 3 months. This pack keeps your child brushing with fresh, hygienic heads for the months ahead. Snap-on design — no tools needed.</p>",
            "alt_bg": false
          }
        },
        "content_3": {
          "type": "content_section",
          "settings": {
            "label": "",
            "heading": "Better Value Than Buying Separately",
            "subheading": "",
            "body": "<p>Purchased individually the toothbrush, toothpaste and replacement heads cost over AED 309. The bundle price of AED 150 saves you more than half — plus you get free next-day delivery across the UAE. It is the smartest way to start or refresh your child's dental care routine. Looking to add an extra brush for a sibling? Increase the quantity above and save even more.</p>",
            "alt_bg": false
          }
        },
        "content_4": {
          "type": "content_section",
          "settings": {
            "label": "",
            "heading": "Free Next-Day Delivery Across the UAE",
            "subheading": "",
            "body": "<p>Order the Kids Dental Care Bundle before 8 PM and receive <strong>free next-day delivery</strong> anywhere in the UAE — Dubai, Abu Dhabi, Sharjah, Ajman, RAK, Fujairah, and Umm Al Quwain. Cash on Delivery available on every order. Not satisfied? Return within 14 days for a full refund.</p>",
            "alt_bg": false
          }
        },
