            "answer": "<p>The bundle includes three items: a <strong>Kids U-Shaped Electric Toothbrush</strong>, a tube of <strong>Kids Strawberry Foam Toothpaste</strong>, and a pack of <strong>Replacement Silicone Brush Heads</strong>. Everything your child needs for a complete oral care routine.</p>"
